t;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1ufs\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模块</span>负责将上述复杂的宏观指令拆解成一步步可执行的子步骤。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1ufs\">中间的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Task 模块</span>负责具体执行 Planner 分配的某一个步骤。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1ufs\">左下角的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Validator 模块</span>是一个反馈机制，用于确认任务是否真的完成了。</span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </ms-cmark-node>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd944\">Validator 的存在确保了每一步都确实完成了才进行下一步，防止 AI 在网页加载失败或操作失误时继续盲目执行。