tion-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 16px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">如何使用</span></span></strong></p>\n   </ms-cmark-node>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fdiuh\">Skyvern 提供了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Python 库和基于 Docker 的独立服务两种主要使用方式</span>。为了体验完整功能，包括 UI 界面，推荐使用 Docker 部署。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1wp9\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">① 部署环境：</span>你需要安装 Docker 和 Docker Desktop。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fdbrv\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">② 快速启动（Docker Compose）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1ib2\">克隆开源项目并启动服务：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 克隆代码</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">git&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">clone</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Skyvern-AI/skyvern.git\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Skyvern-AI/skyvern.git</a></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">cd</span>&nbsp;skyvern</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 初始化配置文件（会生成 .env 文件）</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 此时需要根据提示填入你的 LLM API Key（如 OpenAI 或 Claude 的 Key）</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">./run_skyvern.sh init</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 启动服务</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">docker compose up -d</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fdnb2\">启动成功后，访问浏览器 `<a href=\"http://localhost:8080`\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8080`</a> 即可看到可视化的操作界面。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fdzx7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">③ 通过 Python 代码调用</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd16ph\">如果你希望将它集成到自己的代码中，可以安装 SDK：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">pip</span>&nbsp;install skyvern</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1lga\">简单的代码示例：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"python\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">from</span>&nbsp;skyvern&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">import</span>&nbsp;Skyvern</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 初始化</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">skyvern = Skyvern(api_key=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"你的_SKYVERN_API_KEY\"</span>)&nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 注：如果是本地部署，需配置 base_url 指向本地服务</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 下达任务</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">task =&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">await</span>&nbsp;skyvern.run_task(&nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">prompt=<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"去 Hacker News 网站找到今天热度最高的帖子，并返回标题和链接\"</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">)</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">print</span>(task)</span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"miq251fd1kza\">在运行过程中，你甚至可以通过 UI 界面看到浏览器自动操作的实时画面，非常适合调试和监控。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/Skyvern-AI/skyvern\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Skyvern-AI/skyvern</a></span></code></pre>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Skyvern 是一个基于大模型和计算机视觉的开源项目，旨在通过 AI 理解网页并实现更健壮的浏览器自动化，彻底解决传统 RPA 因页面结构变化而失效的问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Skyvern 是一个基于大模型和计算机视觉的开源项目，旨在通过 AI 理解网页并实现更健壮的浏览器自动化，彻底解决传统 RPA 因页面结构变化而失效的问题。",
  "summary": "文章深入介绍了 GitHub 上备受关注的开源项目 Skyvern，它利用大语言模型和计算机视觉技术，彻底革新了传统 RPA（机器人流程自动化）领域。传统 RPA 工具如 Selenium 或 Puppeteer，极易因网页 UI 元素（如 CSS 类名、XPath）的微小变动而导致脚本失效，维护成本高昂。Skyvern 则通过模拟人类视觉理解网页内容，从而实现对网页的智能操作，摆脱了对固定选择器的依赖，显著提升了自动化脚本的鲁棒性。其核心架构遵循“规划-执行-验证”模式，由 Planner 负责任务分解，Task 执行具体操作，Validator 进行反馈确认，确保任务的可靠完成。文章还提供了详细的 Docker 部署和 Python SDK 使用指南，并附带了在线体验地址，极大降低了开发者的上手门槛。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Skyvern 利用大模型和计算机视觉解决传统 RPA 的脆弱性问题",
      "explanation": "传统 RPA 脚本因依赖硬编码选择器，极易受网页结构变化影响而失效。Skyvern 通过 AI 理解网页内容，实现像人类一样的自动化操作，显著提升了自动化脚本的健壮性与可维护性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "项目核心采用“规划-执行-验证”的 AI 架构保证任务执行的鲁棒性",
      "explanation": "Planner 负责将复杂任务拆解，Task 执行具体操作，Validator 提供反馈机制确保每一步骤的完成，有效避免 AI 盲目执行，提升了自动化流程的可靠性。"
